<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Medical Report: Cardiac Health Evaluation</title>
  <style>
    /* Add your custom styles here */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f2f9fd;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888;
    }
    .span-link{
      color: blue;
    }
    .card {
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f2f9fd;
    }
    /* Color Palette */
    .primary-text {
      color: #333;
    }
    .secondary-text {
      color: #666;
    }
    .primary-bg {
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .accent-bg {
      background-color: #e9f5ff;
    }
    .primary-btn {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .primary-btn:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
    .details{
     color: blue;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .verdict {
      background-color: #d4edda; /* Green background color */
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1 class="primary-text">Medical Report: Cardiac Health Evaluation</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="primary-text">Dear {{userName}},</p>
      <p class="secondary-text">We hope this report finds you well.</p>
      <p class="secondary-text">Following a comprehensive evaluation, your cardiac health diagnosis has been established. Here are the results:</p>
       <div class="verdict">
        <p class="primary-text">Diagnosis: {{predictionResult}}</p>
      </div>
      <p class="secondary-text">To gain insight into your diagnosis or manage your health, try our AI; PalmGPT, specifcally trained to answer questions on heart conditions.<span class="details"> Click the button below to view the detailed assessment:</span></p>
      <div class="button-container">
        <p><a href="http://localhost:5173/login/patient" class="button primary-btn">View Detailed Assessment</a></p>
      </div>
      <p class="secondary-text">For further assistance or inquiries, feel free to contact us at +233 249 300 617 or +233 200 047 855.</p>
      <p class="secondary-text">Report generated by: Dr. {{doctorName}}</p>
      <p class="secondary-text">Patient details:</p>
      <ul class="secondary-text">
        <li>Age: {{userAge}}</li>
        <li>Gender: {{userGender}}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p class="secondary-text">Wishing you continued health and well-being,</p>
      <p class="primary-text">Your Healthcare Team - Palmed Medical Institute</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
